Body: Description: We have an Endpoint Protector test server which we use only for server updates/upgrades prior to rolling out to production. The current Device Control licensing on the test server is expiring soon, which is not needed. Will server updates still be available without any active module licenses?

What We've Learned Updated: 5/13/2025
- Customer asked if they needed a license to continue updating their test server
- Reached out to Team Lead and Sara Hall
- Added Customer Success Team to email thread
- Customer Success mailed customer an extension license
Next Steps Updated: Awaiting Customer response
